{"tha-ap40:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap40:0.2":"Kundadhanavagga ","tha-ap40:0.3":"8 Ayagadayakattheraapadana ","tha-ap40:1.1":"“Nibbute lokanathamhi, ","tha-ap40:1.2":"sikhimhi vadatam vare; ","tha-ap40:1.3":"Hattho hatthena cittena, ","tha-ap40:1.4":"avandim thupamuttamam. ","tha-ap40:2.1":"Vaddhakihi kathapetva, ","tha-ap40:2.2":"mulam datvanaham tada; ","tha-ap40:2.3":"Hattho hatthena cittena, ","tha-ap40:2.4":"ayagam karapesaham. ","tha-ap40:3.1":"Attha kappani devesu, ","tha-ap40:3.2":"abbokinnam vasim aham; ","tha-ap40:3.3":"Avasesesu kappesu, ","tha-ap40:3.4":"vokinnam samsarim aham. ","tha-ap40:4.1":"Kaye visam na kamati, ","tha-ap40:4.2":"satthani na ca hanti me; ","tha-ap40:4.3":"Udakeham na miyyami, ","tha-ap40:4.4":"ayagassa idam phalam. ","tha-ap40:5.1":"Yadicchami aham vassam, ","tha-ap40:5.2":"mahamegho pavassati; ","tha-ap40:5.3":"Devapi me vasam enti, ","tha-ap40:5.4":"punnakammassidam phalam. ","tha-ap40:6.1":"Sattaratanasampanno, ","tha-ap40:6.2":"timsakkhattum ahosaham; ","tha-ap40:6.3":"Na mam kecavajananti, ","tha-ap40:6.4":"punnakammassidam phalam. ","tha-ap40:7.1":"Ekattimse ito kappe, ","tha-ap40:7.2":"ayagam yamakarayim; ","tha-ap40:7.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap40:7.4":"ayagassa idam phalam. ","tha-ap40:8.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap40:8.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap40:8.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap40:9.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma ayagadayako thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap40:10.1":"Ayagadayakattherassapadanam atthamam. "}